author: brian.argabright@delrionewsherald.com(bargabright)
title: Del Rio’s Smith finishes eighth at McNeil meet
text: Brian Argabright Max Smith Del Rio’s Max Smith, seen here at the Del Rio Invitational Flight Cross-Country Meet in August, finished eighth out of 395 runners at the McNeil Invitational Cross-Country Meet Saturday in McAllen. Posted: Sunday, October 4, 2015 1:00 am Del Rio’s Smith finishes eighth at McNeil meet   With the top teams and runners from around the state competing at the annual McNeil Invitational Cross-Country Meet in McAllen this weekend, it wasn’t going to be easy for Del Rio’s teams.
